text=(:Summary:Possible 'future states' for the next few releases of PmWiki:)%0a%25define=done item color=#777%25%0aCurrent PmWiki version is ''{$Version}'' \\%0aThis is the "current best guesses" on upcoming features for PmWiki:%0a%0a!! Features planned for 2.3.x%0a* Add a linkfrom= option to pagelists (with wildcards) - See (PITS:01204)%0a* Allow link= option to do wildcards - see [[Cookbook/PageListMultiTargets]] &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Syntax highlighting of PmWiki markup (documentation, editor) Cookbook:PmSyntax &#10003; %25done%25%0a%0a!! Features planned for 2.2.x%0a%0a* tz= and localization options to [@{(ftime ...)}@] &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Add list=grouphomes option to pagelists &#10003; %25done%25%0a* [@[[ target "title"| text ]]@] markup (PITS:01172) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Add quiet= option to redirects (PITS:00919) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Error messages in [@(:include:)@] (PITS:00652) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Comments (PmForm [[https://www.pmwiki.org/PmForm/Comments|Comments]]; see list [[https://pmichaud.com/pipermail/pmwiki-users/2006-September/032787.html|planning]], [[https://pmichaud.com/pipermail/pmwiki-users/2006-October/033982.html|delay]] and   [[https://pmichaud.com/pipermail/pmwiki-users/2007-May/043581.html|announcement]]) &#10003; %25done%25%0a%0a!! Features added to the 2.2.0 beta series%0a* [[Page text variables]] (2.2.0-beta1) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Extensible [[page list(s)]] (2.2.0-beta13) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Relative links and [[page variables]] in markup text (2.2.0-beta1) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Add an UpdatePage() function for recipes to update pages (2.2.0-beta13) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* [@(:input select ...:)@] markup (PITS:00567) (2.2.0-beta17) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Set default values for input forms (2.2.0-beta17) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Built-in [[blocklist]] capability (2.2.0-beta13) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Leading spaces rule can be disabled (2.2.0-beta41) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Improved [[PmWiki/EditVariables#EnableDrafts|draft]] capabilities (PITS:00755) (2.2.0-beta43) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Set input focus (2.2.0-beta53) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Listing of site-wide permissions settings (AuthList) (2.2.0-beta52) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Improved UTF-8 handling in searches (2.2.0-beta43) &#10003; %25done%25%0a* Move admin pages in Site.* to SiteAdmin group (2.2.0-beta58) &#10003; %25done%25%0a%0a%0a!! Things planned post-2.3.0%0a* add some of the [[Category/core candidate]]s to the PmWiki base%0a* Convert PmWiki default charset to UTF-8%0a* Show search terms in context%0a* Sort search results by relevance%0a** %25green%25 um; don't know if there's already some progress on those; however, not knowing about these plans, I've done something similar myself; if interested, see: [[Cookbook.SortByScore]] (in tandem with [[Cookbook.Excerpts]]) - ''[-(~[[~Mateusz]])-]''%0a* Allow spaces in usernames and authorization groups%0a* Centralized authorization control%0a* Redesign of PageStore and $PCache (likely 2.3 or later)%0a** more efficient searches/indexing%0a** handle non-UTF-8 characters on Mac OS/X%0a** case-insensitive page names on case-sensitive filesystems%0a*** %25green%25 see [[Cookbook.CaseCorrection]] for a platform-independent implementation of this. --[[~Eemeli Aro]]%0a** page names with spaces%0a* Email to wiki gateway%0a** %25green%25 see [[Cookbook.WikiBox]] for an implementation of this. -- [[~Peter Bowers]]%0a* Blogging (PITS:BlogFeatures)%0a* WikiCreole 1.0 support%0a* Better RTL support (from ideas contributed by anyone who can test and report)%0a* Update pagelists to be able to do refcounts%0a* Allow trail= option to pagelist to accept wildcards%0a* Add duplicates=yes option to pagelist (default to duplicates=no)%0a%0a%0aRequests for new features should be added to [[PITS/]], or sent to the [[pmwiki-users mailing list -> MailingLists]].%0a%0aCategories: [[!PmWiki Developer]] (:comment Pages can be add to more categories. It is also pertinent for end-user...:)
